OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774872665
OL,3,CTara Jones makes history as first
OL,4,Cfemale Super League referee
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports sports
OL,7,Fcorrespondent Mike Hall spoke with
OL,8,FTara Jones MBE after she made history
OL,9,Fas the first woman to referee a mens
OL,10,FSuper League game.
OL,12,FThe first woman to ever referee a mens
OL,13,FSuper League game says she "enjoyed
OL,14,Fevery moment" - even if some players
OL,15,Ffound it hard to break old habits.
OL,17,FTaking charge of Wigan's clash with
OL,18,FHuddersfield, trailblazing official
OL,19,FTara Jones revealed that several
OL,20,Fplayers accidentally addressed her as
OL,21,F"sir" during the heat of the match.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774872665
OL,3,CTara Jones makes history as first
OL,4,Cfemale Super League referee
OL,6,F"I understand it's habit," she said.
OL,7,F"They've just got to get used to it.
OL,8,FOne of them acknowledged that at the
OL,9,Fend and I'm sure they will as they get
OL,10,Fused to having me refereeing them."
OL,12,FDespite the slip-ups, Jones praised
OL,13,Fthe "unbelievable" support from both
OL,14,Fclubs.
OL,16,FShe said: "Every single player on the
OL,17,Fpitch shook my hand and said
OL,18,F'congratulations' and 'well done'. I
OL,19,Fcan't thank them enough".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
