OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774872665
OL,3,CTara Jones makes history as first
OL,4,Cfemale Super League referee
OL,6,FThe match capped off a busy week for
OL,7,Fthe official who, just days prior to
OL,8,Fmaking her Super League debut, was
OL,9,Fmade an MBE for her services to rugby
OL,10,Fleague.
OL,12,FShe accepted the honour from the
OL,13,FPrince of Wales at Windsor Castle on
OL,14,FTuesday, 24 March.
OL,16,FThe former St Helens hooker is now
OL,17,Ffocused on ensuring she is not the
OL,18,Flast woman to reach the top flight,
OL,19,Fnoting that several young girls had
OL,20,Fbought tickets specifically to watch
OL,21,Fher officiate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774872665
OL,3,CTara Jones makes history as first
OL,4,Cfemale Super League referee
OL,6,F"If you can see it, you can be it,"
OL,7,Fshe said. "I know for a fact there
OL,8,Fwere girls there today who want to
OL,9,Ftake up officiating or see how it's
OL,10,Fdone at the top level.
OL,12,F"Hopefully, I can inspire those
OL,13,Falready involved to keep going and
OL,14,Fmake it to the top like I have, or
OL,15,Fencourage someone to pick up the
OL,16,Fwhistle and give it a go."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
