PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1774872665
OL,3,CTara Jones makes history as first
OL,4,Cfemale Super League referee
OL,6,FTara became the first woman to be
OL,7,Fappointed to the RFL's full-time match
OL,8,Fofficials squad at the end of 2024 and
OL,9,Fwas the first woman to officiate in a
OL,10,Fsenior men's match when she took
OL,11,Fcharge of the League One game.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
